As travelers, we seek culture, color, and contrast — and sometimes we uncover truths too big to ignore.
Kishangarh’s Dumping Yard isn’t on any itinerary, but it tells a powerful story about urban growth, waste, and the price of progress.
This is the other side of Rajasthan — raw, real, and worth noticing.
